OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FA victim of domestic abusive says she
OL,8,Fis 'petrified' at the release of her
OL,9,Fex partner, who is due to be released
OL,10,Ffrom prison after 11 months.
OL,12,FBekah Smith was in a relationship with
OL,13,FMMA fighter Karl Draper for three
OL,14,Fyears, but says she was 'left fearing
OL,15,Ffor her life' at the levels of abuse
OL,16,Fshe faced.
