OL,4,Cabusive ex partner after 11 month
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FBekah said: "So it started with just
OL,8,Fpushing, shoving, name-calling and the
OL,9,Fby the time I was pregnant he was
OL,10,Fstrangling me, leaving me with black
OL,11,Feyes, bites and bruises."
OL,13,FShe is now calling for laws around
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse to be reformed in the
OL,15,FUK, fearing she will 'bump into him'
OL,16,Fif an 'exclusion zone' is not
OL,17,Fimplemented.
