OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FShe said: "After thee years of
OL,8,Ftorture, my life is worth 11 months of
OL,9,Fjustice... the laws in the UK with
OL,10,Fviolence against women are so outdated.
OL,12,FKarl Draper was jailed last year for
OL,13,Fsix counts of ABH and coercive
OL,14,Fcontrol, but he is preparing to be
OL,15,Freleased after 11 months.
OL,17,FWhile in court, the MMA fighter
OL,18,Fadmitted engaging in controlling or
OL,19,Fcoercive behaviour and five counts of
OL,20,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm.
