OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FHe was sentenced on Monday 4 March
OL,8,F2024 to two years in prison and banned
OL,9,Ffrom contacting his ex-girlfriend for
OL,10,Ffive years.
OL,12,FDuring his sentencing, Liverpool Crown
OL,13,FCourt heard about the "years of abuse"
OL,14,FBekah Smith was subjected to during
OL,15,Fher relationship with Draper.
OL,17,FSome of the worst levels of abuse saw
OL,18,Fhim split open the scar of Bekah's c-
OL,19,Fsection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
