OL,7,FSpeaking about the abuse, Bekah said:
OL,8,F"So I came back from the hospital and
OL,9,Fwithin a matter of days he'd split my
OL,10,FCaesarian scar open with an assault".
OL,12,FBekah made the decision to contact the
OL,13,Fpolice once the abuse started
OL,14,Fhappening while their newborn baby was
OL,15,Fpresent.
OL,17,FBekah also recently took part in a
OL,18,Fmarch in response to the death of
OL,19,FKiena Dawes.
