OL,4,Cabusive ex partner after 11 month
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FRyan Wellings, 30, was cleared of the
OL,8,Funlawful killing of 23-year-old Kiena
OL,9,FDawes, after she left a note calling
OL,10,Fher partner a "monster" who had
OL,11,F"killed me".
OL,13,FShe left the note and their nine-month-
OL,14,Fold daughter with a friend before
OL,15,Fkilling herself on 22 July 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
