OL,4,Cabusive ex partner after 11 month
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FMr Wellings was convicted of assault
OL,8,Fand coercive and controlling behaviour
OL,9,Fover a two-year period, but cleared of
OL,10,Fmanslaughter by the jury on Monday 12
OL,11,FJanuary after a six-week trial at
OL,12,FPreston Crown Court.
OL,14,FBekah said: "It's been really
OL,15,Ftriggering for me to know it could
OL,16,Fhave been me, and knowing that it will
OL,17,Fbe other women".
